title: Opie & Jim Norton OCT 28 2015 Wed.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton OCT 28 2015 Wed (03:13:42)


On Today's Show:

SHERROD SMALL, ANTHONY BOURDAIN & EVANDER HOLYFIELD.


Sherrod Small is with Opie and Jimmy. They talk about last night's baseball game and some other sports things until Anthony Bourdain joins them. They then talk about his TV shows and books and his travels and his life.

They talk about a football who had a fireworks accident months ago, blackface for Halloween, and a couple of stories involving the N word.

Evander Holyfield joins them and they talk about his life and fights
